title: "This is what happens when you don't wake up from anesthesia" | Ulthera #shorts
text:
Employee Welfare Day!
Actually, this video was uploaded last year! Haha
So many people laughed and sympathized back then!

Watching it again, the memories are vivid!

Even the director's actions are so cute and adorable! Haha

It was such an unexpected move that even we, who were filming, were startled... haha

In case anyone is worried!
Sudden movements like this can occur while sleeping, regardless of one's will,
so at the hospital, we gently immobilize and manage hands and feet :)

Also, because we care for a variety of people every day,
we know full well that movements and unexpected reactions during sleep can happen!

Actually, these reactions aren't uncommon,
but rather a natural reaction that varies slightly from person to person.
That's why regular customers
are not at all concerned about their own movements or reactions! Don't feel pressured, haha.

Because we face this as "work,"
we don't find any situation funny or novel,
but simply continue providing care in a familiar, quiet, and safe manner.

The laughter in the video
is simply a reaction born from a friendly relationship with a long-time employee.

I want to make it clear that all care is always based on trust, respect, and sincerity. :)

title: My personal opinion on the 7.5 million won dermatology fee
text:
I'm posting this with the expectation of getting criticized.

I've never heard of a price like this in my entire career.
It feels like an over-the-top procedure to me.
If I were you, I'd recommend something other than the Ulthera + Rejuran combo.
Even celebrities and those with a lot of money should get affordable procedures!
This is my personal opinion, so if you have a different opinion, please leave a comment.
